%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20Dead%2C%20Many%20Critical%20In%20Jaipur%20Fire%20As%202%20Trucks%20Collide%20Outside%20Petrol%20Pump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20seven%20persons%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20massive%20fire%20that%20broke%20out%20following%20a%20truck%20collision%20outside%20a%20petrol%20pump%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jaipur%20this%20morning.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20around%205%3A30%20am%20on%20Ajmer%20Road%20when%20a%20CNG%20tanker%20parked%20near%20the%20petrol%20pump%20caught%20fire%20after%20a%20truck%20collided%20with%20other%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20officials%2C%20more%20people%20are%20feared%20dead%2C%20while%20more%20than%2040%20people%20have%20been%20injured.%20At%20least%2028%20victims%20are%20in%20a%20critical%20condition%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire%20which%20has%20engulfed%20several%20vehicles%20parked%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explosion%20was%20so%20intense%20that%20several%20vehicles%20within%20a%20300-meter%20radius%20were%20engulfed%20and%20completely%20burned%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20IANS.%20Several%20drivers%20were%20reportedly%20burned%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20with%20some%20in%20critical%20condition.%20Visuals%20of%20the%20incident%20show%20a%20massive%20blaze%20and%20a%20cloud%20of%20black%20smoke%20above%20it%20-%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20several%20kilometers%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20locals%2C%20the%20explosion%20was%20heard%20up%20to%2010%20kilometers%20away.%20Reportedly%2C%20there%20were%20also%20repeated%20explosions%20as%20many%20of%20the%20fuel%20tanks%20burst.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20truck%20that%20hit%20the%20other%20vehicles%20was%20reportedly%20loaded%20with%20a%20chemical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fire%20has%20engulfed%20several%20trucks.%20The%20number%20of%20trucks%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%20is%20not%20clear.%20Some%20people%20with%20burn%20injuries%20have%20been%20rushed%20to%20hospitals%20in%20ambulances%2C%26quot%3B%20Station%20House%20Officer%20(SHO)%2C%20Bhankrota%2C%20Manish%20Gupta%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhajanlal%20Sharma%20has%20reached%20the%20hospital%20to%20meet%20the%20victims%20and%20expressed%20condolences%20on%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20deeply%20saddened%20to%20hear%20the%20sad%20news%20of%20casualties%20of%20citizens%20in%20the%20gas%20tanker%20fire%20incident%20on%20Jaipur-Ajmer%20National%20Highway.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20information%20about%20the%20incident%20was%20received%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20went%20to%20SMS%20Hospital%20and%20directed%20the%20doctors%20to%20provide%20immediate%20necessary%20medical%20facilities%20and%20take%20proper%20care%20of%20the%20injured.%20Rescue%20work%20by%20the%20administration%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20local%20administration%20and%20emergency%20services%20are%20working%20with%20full%20readiness.%20I%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20grant%20the%20departed%20souls%20a%20place%20in%20his%20supreme%20abode%2C%20give%20the%20bereaved%20families%20strength%20to%20bear%20this%20immense%20loss%2C%20and%20provide%20speedy%20recovery%20to%20the%20injured%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B7%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%97%20%E0%A4%AA%E0