%20to%20face%20federal%20charges%20including%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuigi%20Mangione's%20arraignment%20took%20place%20hours%20after%20US%20television%20networks%20broadcast%20the%2026-year-old's%20dramatic%20extradition%20by%20plane%20and%20helicopter%20from%20Pennsylvania%2C%20where%20he%20was%20arrested%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20restaurant%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20shackles%20around%20his%20ankles%2C%20Mangione%20appeared%20before%20federal%20judge%20Katharine%20Parker%2C%20who%20read%20out%20the%20charges%20in%20the%20December%204%20shooting%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20chief%20executive%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20including%20murder%2C%20stalking%20and%20firearms%20offenses%2C%20according%20to%20a%20court%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThompson's%20murder%20brought%20to%20the%20surface%20deep%20public%20frustration%20with%20the%20dysfunction%20and%20ills%20of%20the%20lucrative%20US%20commercial%20healthcare%20system%2C%20with%20many%20social%20media%20users%20lionizing%20Mangione.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20Manhattan%20courthouse%2C%20supporters%20held%20posters%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BHealth%20over%20wealth%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BLuigi%20freed%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20James%20Dennehy%20of%20the%20FBI%20New%20York%20Field%20Office%20stressed%20that%20Magione's%20alleged%20actions%20amounted%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcarefully%20premeditated%20and%20targeted%20execution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20alleged%20plot%20demonstrates%20a%20cavalier%20attitude%20towards%20humanity%20--%20deeming%20murder%20an%20appropriate%20recourse%20to%20satiate%20personal%20grievances.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20convicted%2C%20Mangione%20could%20face%20the%20death%20penalty%20or%20life%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20charges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20federal%20charges%20expand%20the%20case%20against%20Ivy%20League%20graduate%20Mangione%2C%20coming%20two%20days%20after%20New%20York%20prosecutors%20filed%20separate%20state%20charges%20against%20him%2C%20including%20one%20count%20of%20murder%20in%20the%20second%20degree%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20act%20of%20terrorism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione's%20attorney%20Karen%20Friedman%20Agnifilo%20told%20reporters%20she%20is%20seeking%20clarity%20on%20how%20simultaneous%20federal%20and%20state%20charges%20would%20work%2C%20calling%20the%20situation%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20unusual%2C%26quot%3B%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione's%20attorneys%20also%20said%20they%20are%20not%20asking%20the%20court%20to%20release%20him%20on%20bail%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now%2C%20according%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20intense%20media%20attention%20the%20case%20has%20garnered%2C%20multiple%20television%20networks%20boasted%20live%20coverage%20of%20his%20trip%20from%20Pennsylvania%20to%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDressed%20in%20an%20orange%20prison%20jumpsuit%2C%20Mangione%20left%20the%20Pennsylvania%20courthouse%20in%20a%20black%20SUV%2C%20escorted%20by%20police%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20flown%20to%20an%20airport%20outside%20New%20York%20City%2C%20he%20boarded%20a%20helicopter%20to%20Manhattan%2C%20where%20over%20a%20dozen%20officers%2C%20some%20in%20tactical%20gear%2C%20waited%20to%20retrieve%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20was%20among%20the%20officials%20escorting%20Mangione.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20act%20of%20terrorism%20and%20the%20violence%20that%20stems%20from%20it%20is%20not%20something%20that%20will%20be%20tolerated%20in%20this%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20told%20reporters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20debate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20was%20arrested%20in%20Altoona%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20on%20December%209%20following%20a%20tip%20from%20staff%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20restaurant%2C%20after