apidly%2C%20more%20and%20more%20couples%20are%20making%20their%20own%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20for%20some%20families%2C%20the%20first%20step%20when%20young%20lovers%20want%20to%20get%20married%20is%20not%20to%20call%20a%20priest%20or%20party%20planner%20but%20a%20sleuth%20like%20Paliwal%20with%20high-tech%20spy%20tools%20to%20investigate%20the%20prospective%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheela%2C%20an%20office%20worker%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20said%20that%20when%20her%20daughter%20announced%20she%20wanted%20to%20marry%20her%20boyfriend%2C%20she%20immediately%20hired%20Paliwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20bad%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sheela%2C%20whose%20name%20has%20been%20changed%20as%20her%20daughter%20remains%20unaware%20her%20fiance%20was%20spied%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20daughter%20said%20she's%20in%20love%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20support%20her%20--%20but%20not%20without%20proper%20checks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaliwal%2C%2048%2C%20who%20founded%20her%20Tejas%20Detective%20Agency%20more%20than%20two%20decades%20ago%2C%20says%20business%20is%20better%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20team%20handles%20around%20eight%20cases%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20recent%20case%20--%20a%20client%20checking%20her%20prospective%20husband%20--%20Paliwal%20discovered%20a%20decimal%20point%20salary%20discrepancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20man%20said%20he%20earns%20around%20%2470%2C700%20annually%2C%26quot%3B%20Paliwal%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20found%20out%20he%20was%20actually%20making%20%247%2C070.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Service%20to%20society'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20discreet%20work.%20Paliwal's%20office%20is%20tucked%20away%20in%20a%20city%20mall%2C%20with%20an%20innocuous%20sign%20board%20saying%20it%20houses%20an%20astrologer%20--%20a%20service%20families%20often%20use%20to%20predict%20an%20auspicious%20wedding%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20my%20clients%20also%20don't%20want%20people%20to%20know%20they%20are%20meeting%20a%20detective%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20laughed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiring%20a%20detective%20can%20cost%20from%20%24100%20to%20%242%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20extent%20of%20surveillance%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20a%20small%20investment%20for%20families%20who%20splash%20out%20many%20times%20more%20on%20the%20wedding%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20worried%20parents%20trying%20to%20vet%20their%20prospective%20sons%20or%20daughters-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20want%20background%20checks%20on%20their%20future%20spouse%20--%20or%2C%20after%20marriage%2C%20to%20confirm%20a%20suspected%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20service%20to%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20a%2051-year-old%20sleuth%2C%20who%20says%20his%20agency%20has%20handled%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%26quot%3B%20of%20pre-matrimonial%20investigations%20this%20year%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20eye%20Akriti%20Khatri%20said%20around%20a%20quarter%20of%20cases%20at%20her%20Venus%20Detective%20Agency%20were%20pre-marriage%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20people%20who%20want%20to%20know%20if%20the%20groom%20is%20actually%20gay%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20citing%20one%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArranged%20marriages%20binding%20two%20entire%20families%20together%20require%20a%20chain%20of%20checks%20before%20the%20couple%20even%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20financial%20probes%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20their%20status%20in%20India's%20millennia-old%20caste%20hierarchy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarriages%20breaking%20rigid%20caste%20or%20religious%20divisions%20can%20have%20deadly%20repercussions%2C%20sometimes%20resulting%20in%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bhonour%26quot%3B%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20such%20premarital%20checks%20were%20often%20done%20by%20family%20members%2C%20priests%20or%20professional%20matchmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20breakneck%20urbanisation%20in%20sprawling%20megacities%20has%20shaken%20social%20networks%2C%20challenging%20conventional%20ways%20of%20verifying%20marriage%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArranged%20marriages%20now%20also%20happen%20online%20through%20matchmaking%20websites%2C%20or%20even%20dating%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarriage%20proposals%20come%20on%20Tinder%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Basis%20of%20lies'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20is%20not%20without%20its%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELayers%20of%20security%20in%20guarded%20modern%20apartment%20blocks%20mean%20it%20is%20often%20far%20harder%20for%20an%20agent%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20a%20property%20than%20older%20standalone%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20detectives%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20their%20charm%20to%20tell%20a%20%26quot%3Bcock%20and%20bull%20story%26quot%3B%20to%20enter%2C%20saying%20his%20teams%20tread%20the%20grey%20zone%20between%20%26quot%3Blegal%20and%20illegal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20stressed%20his%20agents%20operate%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20law%2C%20ordering%20his%20teams%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20unethical%26quot%3B%20while%20noting%20investigations%20often%20mean%20%26quot%3Bsomebody's%20life%20is%20getting%20ruined%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnology%20is%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20sleuths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhatri%20has%20used%20tech%20developers%20to%20create%20an%20app%20for%20her%20agents%20to%20upload%20records%20directly%20online%20--%20leaving%20nothing%20on%20agents'%20phones%2C%20in%20case%20they%20are%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20safer%20for%20our%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20also%20helped%20them%20%26quot%3Bget%20sharp%20results%20in%20less%20time%20and%20cost%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurveillance%20tools%20starting%20at%20only%20a%20few%20dollars%20are%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20include%20audio%20and%20video%20recording%20devices%20hidden%20in%20everyday%20items%20such%20as%20mosquito%20repellent%20socket%20devices%2C%20to%20more%20sophisticated%20magnetic%20GPS%20car%20trackers%20or%20tiny%20wearable%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20boom%2C%20Paliwal%20said%2C%20has%20put%20relationships%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20hi-tech%20we%20become%2C%20the%20more%20problems%20we%20have%20in%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20insisted%20that%20neither%20the%20technology%20nor%20the%20detectives%20should%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20exposing%20a%20cheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20relationships%20would%20not%20have%20lasted%20anyway%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20relationship%20can%20work%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20lies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734670440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F9bhkrf0o_wedding_625x300_20_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbride-groom-spy-how-wedding-detectives-are-running-matrimonial-industry-7291019%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20an%20anonymous%20office%20in%20a%20New%20Delhi%20mall%2C%20matrimonial%20detective%20Bhavna%20Paliwal%20runs%20the%20rule%20over%20prospective%20husbands%20and%20wives%20--%20a%20booming%20industry%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20CEO%20updates%20on%20job%20cuts%20in%20town%20hall%3A%2010%25%20management%20roles%20cut%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734670370000%2C%22vi