quot%3B%3A%20RSS%20Chief%20Frowns%20Upon%20New%20Temple-Mosque%20Disputes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20resurgence%20of%20several%20temple-mosque%20disputes%20and%20said%20certain%20individuals%2C%20after%20the%20construction%20of%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20temple%2C%20seem%20to%20believe%20they%20can%20become%20%E2%80%9Cleaders%20of%20Hindus%E2%80%9D%20by%20raking%20up%20such%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20a%20lecture%20on%20%E2%80%98India%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Vishwaguru'%2C%20at%20Sahjeevan%20Vyakhyanmala%20(lecture%20series)%20in%20Pune%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20advocated%20for%20an%20inclusive%20society%20and%20said%20the%20world%20needs%20to%20be%20shown%20that%20the%20country%20can%20live%20together%20in%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20plurality%20of%20Indian%20society%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20said%20Christmas%20is%20celebrated%20in%20Ramakrishna%20Mission%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3Bonly%20we%20can%20do%20this%20because%20we%20are%20Hindus%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20living%20in%20harmony%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20provide%20this%20harmony%20to%20the%20world%2C%20we%20need%20to%20create%20a%20model%20of%20it.%20After%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20some%20people%20think%20they%20can%20become%20leaders%20of%20Hindus%20by%20raking%20up%20similar%20issues%20in%20new%20places.%20This%20is%20not%20acceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-peace-and-harmony-supreme-court-halts-any-action-on-sambhal-mosque-survey-7132013%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWant%20Peace%20And%20Harmony%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Halts%20Any%20Action%20On%20Sambhal%20Mosque%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20temple%20was%20constructed%20since%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20faith%20for%20all%20Hindus%2C%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20a%20new%20matter%20(dispute)%20is%20being%20raked%20up.%20How%20can%20this%20be%20allowed%3F%20This%20cannot%20continue.%20India%20needs%20to%20show%20that%20we%20can%20live%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20without%20mentioning%20any%20particular%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20demands%20for%20surveys%20of%20mosques%20to%20unearth%20temples%20have%20found%20their%20way%20to%20courts%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20though%20Mr%20Bhagwat%20did%20not%20mention%20any%20by%20name%20in%20his%20lecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20groups%20that%20came%20from%20outside%20brought%20with%20them%20staunchness%20and%20they%20want%20their%20old%20rule%20to%20return%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20now%20the%20country%20runs%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution.%20In%20this%20setup%2C%20people%20choose%20their%20representatives%2C%20who%20run%20the%20government.%20The%20days%20of%20hegemony%20are%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fallahabad-high-court-reopens-mathura-land-dispute-case-after-reserving-order-5797437%5C%22%3EAllahabad%20High%20Court%20Reopens%20Mathura%20Land%20Dispute%20Case%20After%20Reserving%20Order%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20rule%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20was%20characterised%20by%20such%20staunchness%2C%20though%20his%20descendant%20Bahadur%20Shah%20Zafar%20in%201857%20banned%20cow%20slaughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20decided%20that%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20should%20be%20given%20to%20Hindus%20but%20the%20British%20sensed%20it%20and%20created%20a%20rift%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%20Since%20then%2C%20this%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ealgavwad%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(separatism)%20came%20into%20being.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Pakistan%20cam