nameplate%20project%20for%20women%20to%20give%20them%20the%20recognition%20they%20deserved%20for%20their%20contribution%20to%20their%20families%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWomen%20have%20long%20been%20denied%20recognition%20for%20their%20contributions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20manage%20households%2C%20raise%20children%2C%20and%20contribute%20to%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363502%2Firis-strill-bishwadeep-moitra-silaiwali-upcycled-ragdolls-empower-afghan-women-refugees-financial-freedom%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamilies%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20yet%20their%20efforts%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20By%20placing%20women%E2%80%99s%20names%20on%20doorplates%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20them%20the%20recognition%20and%20dignity%20they%20deserve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bhullar%20and%20a%20few%20other%20women%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sheshandeep%20executed%20her%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20confident%20that%20I%20had%20the%20support%20of%20my%20team%2C%20and%20with%20the%20available%20funds%2C%20we%20could%20bring%20my%20plan%20to%20life.%20The%20idea%20of%20adding%20nameplates%20for%20women%20was%20within%20our%20budget.%20So%2C%20we%20swiftly%20moved%20forward%2C%20using%20the%20resources%20already%20allocated%20to%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20110%20households%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20saw%20the%20nameplates%20of%20women%20proudly%20displayed%20on%20every%20door%20in%20the%20village.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate%20and%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20one%20young%20woman%20who%20came%20to%20me%2C%20with%20tears%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20thanking%20me%20for%20this%20initiative.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20never%20been%20allowed%20to%20leave%20her%20home%20or%