2ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Government%20shutdown%20looms%20as%20Trump-backed%20bill%20fails%20to%20pass%20House%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734662413000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fb1b5%2Flive%2Fe17baec0-be38-11ef-a761-a90dfaf55a88.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6l9e3jq7xo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dozens%20of%20Republicans%20defied%20Trump%20and%20joined%20Democrats%20to%20reject%20a%20revised%20spending%20bill.%20Here%20are%20five%20things%20to%20know%20ahead%20of%20Friday%E2%80%99s%20shutdown%20deadline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A69%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6l9e3jq7xo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6l9e3jq7xo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6l9e3jq7xo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20Don't%20Want%20To%20Throw%20Out%20Tainted%20Staff%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Slams%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20questioned%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20why%20it%20had%20created%20supernumerary%20posts%20of%20teachers%20and%20non-teaching%20staff%20instead%20of%20weeding%20out%20persons%20who%20were%20allegedly%20appointed%20illegally.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20you%20create%20supernumerary%20posts%3F%20What%20was%20the%20purpose%20of%20creating%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20asked%20the%20West%20Bengal%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Rakesh%20Dwivedi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20informed%20the%20bench%20about%20a%20report%20by%20a%20committee%20appointed%20for%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20into%20the%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20observed%20the%20committee's%20report%20and%20noted%20some%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dwivedi%20argued%20the%20committee%20found%20some%20irregularities%20but%20not%20as%20extensive%20as%20the%20CBI's%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20they%20found%20there%20were%20irregularities%20committed.%20So%2C%20in%20order%20to%20deal%20with%20that%20situation%2C%20instead%20of%20weeding%20out%20the%20persons%20who%20have%20been%20appointed%20illegally%2C%20you%20say%2C%20okay%20create%20supernumerary%20posts%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Dwivedi%2C%20tell%20me%20one%20thing%2C%20if%20you%20find%20the%20irregularity%20committed%2C%20will%20you%20not%20throw%20them%20out%20first%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20asked%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dwivedi%20said%20the%20order%20had%20specifically%20mentioned%20it%20was%20for%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20wait-listed%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCorrect.%20The%20reason%20is%20this%2C%20that%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20throw%20out%20the%20tainted%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20was%20hearing%20arguments%20on%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20challenging%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20April%2022%20decision%20invalidating%20the%20appointment%20of%2025%2C753%20teachers%20and%20non-teaching%20staff%20in%20state-run%20and%20state-aided%20schools%20of%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%207%2C%20the%20top%20court%20stayed%20the%20high%20court's%20order%20over%20the%20appointments%20made%20by%20the%20state's%20School%20Service%20Commission%20(SSC).%20The%20top%20court%2C%20however%2C%20permitted%20the%20CBI%20to%20continue%20with%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20May%207%20order%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20noted%20that%20on%20May%2019%2C%202022%2C%20the%20state%20government%20issued%20an%20order%20creating%206%2C861%20supernumerary%20posts%20of%20teachers%20and%20non-teaching%20staff%20to%20absorb%20the%20wait-listed%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20further%20noted%20it%20was%20directed%20that%20appointment%20letters%20to%20such%20wait-listed%20candidates%20should%20be%20issued%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20SSC%20subject%20to%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20pending%20litigation%20before%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20bench%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20the%20state%20of%20West%20Bengal%20supporting%20the%20proposition%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20segregate%20the%20tainted%20from%20the%20untainted%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dwivedi%20however%20said%20the%20state%20was%20supporting%20the%20segregation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20the%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20%26quot%3Bwent%20too%20far%20ahead%26quot%3B%20and%20passed%20a%20%26quot%3Bblanket%20direction%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20CBI%20should%20investigate%20everybody%20and%20undertake%20custodial%20interrogation%2C%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20wondered%20why%20the%20original%20OMR%20sheets%20were%20not%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20original%20paper%20is%20the%20OMR%20sheet.%20That%20is%20the%20primary%20evidence.%20If%20any%20manipulation%20is%20done%20on%20the%20main%20evidence%20or%20the%20main%20paper%2C%20it%20will%20be%20only%20visible%20in%20the%20OMR%20sheets%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20would%20be%2C%20because%20the%20originals%20are%20not%20available%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20way%20we%20can%20authenticate%20whether%20the%20original%20OMR%20sheets%20were%20identical%20to%20the%20scanned%20OMR%20sheets%20which%20are%20available%20on%20the%20server%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20asked%20the%20CBI's%20counsel%20whether%20the%20probe%20agency%20was%20able%20to%20ascertain%20the%20date%20on%20which%20the%20OMR%20data%20was%20captured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20is%20very%20strange%20that%20people%20who%20are%20not%20even%20recommended%20and%20who%20have%20not%20qualified...%20they%20were%20issued%20letters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20observed%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20a%20very%20serious%20thing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20day-long%20hearing%2C%20the%20bench%20heard%20submissions%20from%20senior%20advocates%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20Shyam%20Divan%2C%20Jaideep%20Gupta%2C%20Sanjay%20Hegde%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20would%20continue%20in%20January%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%207%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20said%20the%20CBI's%20investigation%2C%20which%20was%20ordered%20by%20the%20high%20court%2C%20would%20continue%20but%20no%20coercive%20steps%20would%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20however%2C%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20teachers%20and%20non-teaching%20staff%20of%20the%20state%2C%20whose%20appointments%20were%20cancelled%20by%20the%20high%20court%2C%20would%20have%20to%20refund%20their%20salaries%20and%20other%20emoluments%20if%20their%20recruitment%20was%20found%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2023%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20state-level%20selection%20test-2016%20for%2024%2C640%20vacant%20posts.%20A%20total%20of%2025%2C753%20appointment%20letters%20were%20issued%20against%2024%2C640%20vacancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734662220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fk7nb8ha_supreme-court_625x300_18_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fssc-recruitment-scam-you-dont-want-to-throw-out-tainted-staff-supreme-court-slams-bengal-7