%20Appeals%20for%20the%20North%20Circuit%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Rana%20on%20November%2013%20filed%20a%20%26quot%3Bpetition%20for%20a%20writ%20of%20certiorari%26quot%3B%20before%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20long%20battle%2C%20this%20is%20Rana's%20last%20legal%20chance%20to%20avoid%20extradition%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%20currently%20lodged%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20faces%20charges%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20and%20is%20known%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20Pakistani-American%20terrorist%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20conspirators%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petition%20for%20a%20writ%20of%20certiorari%20should%20be%20denied%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Solicitor%20General%20Elizabeth%20B%20Prelogar%20said%20in%20its%20filing%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20December%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20relief%20from%20extradition%20to%20India%20in%20this%20case%2C%20she%20argued%20in%20a%2020-page%20submission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%26quot%3Bpetition%20for%20a%20writ%20of%20certiorari%20to%20review%20the%20judgment%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20for%20the%20Ninth%20Circuit%26quot%3B%2C%20Rana%20has%20argued%20that%20he%20was%20tried%20and%20acquitted%20in%20the%20federal%20court%20in%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Illinois%20(Chicago)%20on%20charges%20relating%20to%20the%202008%20terrorist%20attack%20on%20Mumbai.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20now%20seeks%20to%20extradite%20him%20for%20trial%20on%20charges%20based%20on%20the%20identical%20conduct%20at%20issue%20in%20the%20Chicago%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20plea%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrelogar%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20does%20not%20concede%20that%20all%20of%20the%20conduct%20on%20which%20India%20seeks%20extradition%20was%20covered%20by%20the%20government's%20prosecution%20in%20this%20case.%20For%20example%2C%20India's%20forgery%20charges%20are%20based%20in%20part%20on%20conduct%20that%20was%20not%20charged%20in%20the%20United%20States%3A%20petitioner's%20use%20of%20false%20information%20in%20an%20application%20to%20formally%20open%20a%20branch%20office%20of%20the%20Immigration%20Law%20Centre%20submitted%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20solicitor%20general%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20clear%20that%20the%20jury's%20verdict%20in%20this%20case%20--%20which%20involves%20conspiracy%20charges%20and%20was%20somewhat%20difficult%20to%20parse%20--%20means%20that%20he%20has%20been%20'convicted%20or%20acquitted'%20on%20all%20of%20the%20specific%20conduct%20that%20India%20has%20charged%2C%26quot%3B%20Prelogar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20166%20people%2C%20including%20six%20Americans%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%20which%2010%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20laid%20a%20more%20than%2060-hour%20siege%2C%20attacking%20and%20killing%20people%20at%20iconic%20and%20vital%20locations%20of%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734660540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fik9apsg_tahawwur-rana-2008-mumbai-terror-attack-ani_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-government-urges-supreme-court-to-dismiss-mumbai-attack-convict-tahawwur-ranas-petition-against-extradition-to-india-7285320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20United%20States%20government%20has%20urged%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20dismiss%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20Mumbai-attack%20convict%20Tahawwur%20Rana%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%20of%20Pakistani%20origin%2C%20to%20avoid%20his%20extradition%20to%20I