s.%20The%20officials%20found%20that%20the%20available%20electricity%20connection%20was%20one-eighth%20of%20the%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20State%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsamajwadi-party-sambhal-mp-zia-ur-rehman-barq-charged-for-alleged-electricity-theft-7284040%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElectricity%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Barq%20has%20taken%20a%202%20kilowatt%20(kW)%20connection%20whereas%2C%20the%20load%20is%2016.5%20kW.%20The%20new%20smart%20meters%20installed%20two%20days%20ago%20showed%20a%20power%20load%20of%205.5%20kW.%20Mr%20Barq's%20family%20members%20said%20they%20have%20installed%20a%2010%20kW%20solar%20panel%20and%205%20kW%20generator%20in%20the%20house%20-%20with%20which%20the%20MP's%20house%20can%20take%20up%20to%2019%20kW%20electricity%20load.%20However%2C%20the%20Superintending%20Engineer%20of%20the%20Electricity%20Department%20said%20that%20the%20solar%20panels%20at%20the%20residence%20were%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20also%20found%20heavy%20electrical%20appliances%20at%20the%20residence%20including%20over%2050%20LED%20bulbs%2C%20a%20deep%20freezer%2C%20three%20split%20ACs%2C%202%20fridges%2C%20a%20coffee%20maker%2C%20a%20geyser%2C%20and%20a%20microwave%20oven%20-%20which%20were%20found%20to%20have%20an%20electrical%20load%20of%2016%2C480%20kW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20found%20that%20the%20electricity%20bill%20at%20the%20MP's%20residence%20has%20been%20zero%20for%20the%20last%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20was%20filed%20under%20Section%20135%20of%20the%20Anti-Power%20Theft%20Act%20against%20the%20Samajwadi%20MP%2C%20who%20also%20serves%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20District%20Electricity%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electricity%20connection%20at%20the%20MP's%20house%20was%20cut%20off%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20investigation%2C%20the%20MP's%20father%2C%20Mamluk%20Ur%20Re