0promising%2C%20prompting%20discussions%20among%20fans%20and%20experts%20over%20his%20future%20with%20the%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Kohli%20had%20spoken%20of%20the%20retirement%20subject%2C%20suggesting%20once%20he%20calls%20it%20quits%2C%20people%20aren't%20going%20to%20see%20him%20for%20a%20while.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20simple%2C%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20had%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20RCB.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20as%20a%20sportsman%2C%20we%20do%20have%20an%20end-date%20to%20our%20careers.%20So%20I%20am%20just%20working%20backwards.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20finish%20my%20career%20thinking%20'oh%2C%20what%20if%20I%20have%20done%20this%20on%20that%20particular%20day'%20because%20I%20can't%20keep%20going%20on%20and%20on%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20just%20about%20not%20leaving%20any%20undone%20business%20behind%20and%20not%20have%20any%20regrets%20later%2C%20which%20I%20am%20sure%20I%20won't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20I%20am%20done%2C%20I%20will%20be%20gone%2C%20you%20won't%20see%20me%20for%20a%20while%20(smiles).%20So%20I%20want%20to%20give%20it%20everything%20I%20have%20till%20the%20time%20I%20play%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20keeps%20me%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734658500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fu9mgdi18_virat-kohli-and-anushka-sharma-insta_625x300_19_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-leaving-india-set-to-move-to-uk-with-wife-anushka-sharma-and-kids-7284376%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli's%20childhood%20coach%20Rajkumar%20Sharma%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20India%20stalwart%20is%20planning%20to%20move%20to%20the%20UK%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Ashwi