lso%20being%20a%20rare%20setting%20in%20which%20Putin%20is%20put%20on%20the%20spot%20with%20some%20uncomfortable%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20spoke%20for%20just%20under%20four%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Trump's%20overtures%20regarding%20a%20possible%20peace%20deal%2C%20Putin%20said%20he%20would%20welcome%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20incoming%20Republican.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20when%20I'm%20going%20to%20see%20him.%20He%20isn't%20saying%20anything%20about%20it.%20I%20haven't%20talked%20to%20him%20in%20more%20than%20four%20years.%20I%20am%20ready%20for%20it%2C%20of%20course.%20Any%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20ever%20have%20a%20meeting%20with%20President-elect%20Trump%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20we'll%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20talk%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Russia%20was%20ready%20for%20%26quot%3Bnegotiations%20and%20compromises%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKursk%20offensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20troops%20have%20been%20advancing%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%20for%20months%2C%20with%20Putin%20repeatedly%20touting%20their%20prowess%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20asked%20by%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20Kursk%20region%20when%20residents%20would%20be%20able%20to%20return%20to%20their%20homes%20there%2C%20after%20thousands%20were%20evacuated%20from%20frontline%20areas%20during%20the%20Ukrainian%20assault%2C%20Putin%20said%20he%20could%20not%20name%20a%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20absolutely%20kick%20them%20out.%20Absolutely.%20It%20can't%20be%20any%20other%20way.%20But%20the%20question%20of%20a%20specific%20date%2C%20I'm%20sorry%2C%20I%20cannot%20say%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20was%20also%20pressed%20on%20the%20economic%20headwinds%20Russia%20faced%20--%20the%20fallout%20from%20a%20huge%20ramp-up%20in%20military%20spending%20and%20deep%20labour%20shortages%20caused%20by%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20insisted%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20%26quot%3Bstable%2C%20despite%20external%20threats%26quot%3B%2C%20citing%20low%20unemployment%20and%20industrial%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20soaring%20inflation%2C%20Putin%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Binflation%20is%20a%20worrying%20signal%26quot%3B.%20Price%20rises%20for%20foods%20such%20as%20butter%20and%20meat%20were%20%26quot%3Bunpleasant%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20conceded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%2C%20too%2C%20that%20Western%20sanctions%20were%20a%20factor%20--%20while%20not%20of%20%26quot%3Bkey%20significance%26quot%3B.%20He%20hoped%20the%20central%20bank%2C%20expected%20to%20raise%20interest%20rates%20again%20Friday%20to%20cool%20inflation%2C%20would%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bbalanced%26quot%3B%20decision%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOreshnik%20'duel'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20appeared%20to%20repeat%20his%20threat%20to%20strike%20Kyiv%20with%20Russia's%20new%20hypersonic%20ballistic%20missile%2C%20dubbed%20Oreshnik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20a%20military%20journalist%20if%20the%20weapon%20had%20any%20flaws%2C%20Putin%20suggested%20a%20%26quot%3Bhi-tech%20duel%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20West%20and%20Russia%20to%20test%20his%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20impervious%20to%20air%20defences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20them%20set%20some%20target%20to%20be%20hit%2C%20let's%20say%20in%20Kyiv%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20will%20concentrate%20there%20all%20their%20air%20defences.%20And%20we%20will%20launch%20an%20Oreshnik%20strike%20there%20and%20see%20what%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20hit%20back%20by%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20dying%20and%20he%20thinks%20it's%20'interesting'..%20Dumbass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20condemned%20as%20%26quot%3Bterrorism%26quot%3B%20the