0study%20analyzed%20Stack%20Overflow%20and%20found%20that%20traffic%20to%20this%20site%20declined%20by%20about%2012%25%20after%20the%20release%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%20of%20going%20to%20Stack%20Overflow%20to%20ask%20coding%20questions%20and%20do%20research%2C%20some%20developers%20were%20just%20asking%20ChatGPT%20for%20the%20answers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20findings%20from%20the%20research%20Balaji%20cited%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20was%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20number%20of%20questions%20posted%20on%20Stack%20Overflow%20after%20the%20release%20of%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20average%20account%20age%20of%20the%20question-askers%20rose%20after%20ChatGPT%20came%20out%2C%20suggesting%20fewer%20people%20signed%20up%20to%20Stack%20Overflow%20or%20that%20more%20users%20left%20the%20online%20community.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20suggests%20that%20AI%20models%20could%20undermine%20some%20of%20the%20incentives%20that%20created%20the%20information-rich%20internet%20as%20we%20know%20it%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20people%20can%20get%20their%20answers%20directly%20from%20AI%20models%2C%20there's%20no%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20original%20sources%20of%20the%20information.%20If%20people%20don't%20visit%20websites%20as%20much%2C%20advertising%20and%20subscription%20revenue%20may%20fall%2C%20and%20there%20would%20be%20less%20money%20to%20fund%20the%20creation%20and%20verification%20of%20high-quality%20online%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226985064c-d2a7-4deb-98d9-f6156801a8ff%5C%22%3EMKBHD%20wants%20to%20opt%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20even%20more%20galling%20to%20imagine%20that%20AI%20models%20might%20be%20doing%20this%20based%20partly%20on%20your%20own%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20reviewer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarques-brownlee-openai-sora-youtube-ai-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarques%20Brownlee%3C%2Fa%3E%20experienced%20this%20recently%20when%20he%20reviewed%20OpenAI's%20Sora%20video%20model%20and%20found%20that%20it%20created%20a%20clip%20with%20a%20plant%20that%20looked%20a%20lot%20like%20a%20plant%20from%20his%20own%20videos%20posted%20on%20YouTube.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20my%20videos%20in%20that%20source%20material%3F%20Is%20this%20exact%20plant%20part%20of%20the%20source%20material%3F%20Is%20it%20just%20a%20coincidence%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Brownlee%2C%20who's%20known%20as%20MKBHD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20he%20also%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20he%20could%20opt%20out%20and%20prevent%20his%20videos%20from%20being%20used%20to%20train%20AI%20models.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20if%20it's%20too%20late%20to%20opt%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Brownlee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278dc0e84-b49d-4e69-8333-541dfecb5d88%5C%22%3E'Not%20a%20sustainable%20model'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20published%20in%20October%2C%20Balaji%20said%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20ChatGPT%20are%20stripping%20away%20the%20commercial%20value%20of%20people's%20work%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20publication%20reported%20that%20while%20working%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20Balaji%20was%20part%20of%20a%20team%20that%20collected%20data%20from%20the%20internet%20for%20AI%20model%20training.%20He%20joined%20the%20startup%20with%20high%20hopes%20for%20how%20AI%20could%20help%20society%2C%20but%20became%20disillusioned%2C%20NYT%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20sustainable%20model%20for%20the%20internet%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Times%20about%20Balaji's%20comments%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20the%20way%20it%20builds%20AI%20models%20is%20protected%20by%20fair%20use%20copyright%20principles%20and%20supported%20by%20legal%20precedents.%20%26quot%3BWe%20view%20this%20principle%20as%20fair%20to%20creators%2C%20necessary%20for%20innovators%2C%20and%20critical%20for%20US%20competitiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20essay%2C%20Balaji%20disagreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20four%20tests%20for%20copyright%20infringement%20is%20whether%20a%20new%20work%20impacts%20the%C2%A0potential%20market%20for%2C%20or%20value%20of%2C%20the%20original%20copyrighted%20work.%20If%20it%20does%20this%20type%20of%20damage%2C%20then%20it's%20not%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfair%C2%A0use%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20not%20allowed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaji%20concluded%20that%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI%20models%20don't%20quality%20for%20fair%20use%20copyright%20protection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20four%20factors%20seem%20to%20weigh%20in%20favor%20of%20ChatGPT%20being%20a%20fair%20use%20of%20its%20training%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThat%20being%20said%2C%20none%20of%20the%20arguments%20here%20are%20fundamentally%20specific%20to%20ChatGPT%20either%2C%20and%20similar%20arguments%20could%20be%20made%20for%20many%20generative%20AI%20products%20in%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20domains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b52c6b2-9bb9-42a7-a929-9a5a1f2181e8%5C%22%3ETalking%20about%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20producing%20these%20powerful%20AI%20models%20don't%C2%A0like%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20value%20of%20training%20data.%20They've%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-llama-2-data-train-ai-models-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estopped%20disclosing%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they%20get%20the%20data%20from%2C%20which%20was%20a%20common%20practice%20until%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20always%20highlight%20their%20clever%20algorithms%2C%20not%20the%20underlying%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Nick%20Vincent%2C%20an%20AI%20researcher%2C%20told%20BI%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalaji's%20death%20may%20finally%20give%20this%20debate%20the%20attention%20it%20deserves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20devastated%20to%20learn%20of%20this%20incredibly%20sad%20news%20today%20and%20our%20hearts%20go%20out%20to%20Suchir's%20loved%20ones%20during%20this%20difficult%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20recently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20or%20someone%20you%20know%20is%20experiencing%20depression%20or%20has%20had%20thoughts%20of%20harming%20themself%20or%20taking%20their%20own%20life%2C%20get%20help.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20call%20or%20text%20988%20to%20reach%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F988lifeline.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20Suicide%20%26amp%3B%20Crisis%20Lifeline%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20which%20provides%2024%2F7%2C%20free%2C%20confidential%20support%20for%20people%20in%20distress%2C%20as%20well%20as%20best%20practices%20for%20professionals%20and%20resources%20to%20aid%20in%20prevention%20and%20crisis%20situations.%20Help%20is%20also%20available%20through%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisistextline.org%2Ftext-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ECrisis%20Text%20Line%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20just%20text%20%26quot%3BHOME%26quot%3B%20to%20741741.%20The%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffindahelpline.com%2Fi%2Fiasp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EInternational%20Association%20for%20Suicide%20Prevention%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20offers%20resources%20for%20those%20outside%20the%20US.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuchir-balaji-marques-brownlee-openai-ai-training-data-death-llm-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2