shant%20Berma%2C%20noticed%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20locally%20grown%20peanuts.%20This%20sparked%20their%20curiosity%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20peanut%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20while%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20eating%20peanuts%2C%20we%20started%20talking%20about%20their%20great%20quality.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20out%20and%20do%20some%20research%20to%20see%20what%20was%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sushant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20major%20challenge%20faced%20by%20Unnao%E2%80%99s%20groundnut%20farmers%20was%20the%20extremely%20low%20prices%20they%20received%20for%20their%20produce.%20These%20farmers%20were%20forced%20to%20sell%20their%20groundnuts%20for%20a%20mere%20Rs%2030%20to%20Rs%2040%20per%20kilogram%2C%20without%20any%20government%20support%20or%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20recognition%20in%20agricultural%20surveys%20lists%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20issue.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20these%20farmers%20were%20deprived%20of%20essential%20support%20programmes%2C%20hindering%20their%20ability%20to%20earn%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%E2%80%99s%20research%20unveiled%20a%20potential%20solution%3A%20empowering%20farmers%20to%20undertake%20primary%20processing%20themselves.%20By%20handling%20tasks%20like%20shelling%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20grading%2C%20farmers%20could%20significantly%20increase%20their%20earnings%20by%2050-60%25.%20To%20realise%20this%20vision%2C%20Aman%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20State%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%20(UPSRLM)%20seeking%20support%20for%20establishing%20a%20producer%20group%20dedicated%20to%20primary%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Aman%E2%80%99s%20proposal%2C%20the%20Government%20provided%20a%20grant%20that%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20set%20up%20facilities%20for%20shelling%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20grading%20groundnuts.%20This%20primary%20processing%20would%20enable%20farmers%20to%20retain%20a%20higher%20portion%20of%20the%20profits.%20By%20working%20collectively%2C%20the%20farmers%20could%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20produce%20and%20access%20better%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20fresh%20produce%20delivery%20service%20in%202020%20evolved%20into%20Nutty%20Village%20in%202022.%20With%20a%20vision%20to%20empower%20farmers%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20aims%20to%20help%20them%20establish%20their%20own%20processing%20units%2C%20directly%20sourcing%20high-quality%20produce%20at%20fair%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20champion%20both%20the%20exceptional%20products%20these%20farmers%20create%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270093%2Fpeanut-jaggery-health-benefits-indian-food-recipe-for-chikki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20proteins%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20through%20our%20peanut%20butters%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUplifting%20rural%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20farmers%20had%20set%20up%20their%20primary%20processing%20units%2C%20Aman%20started%20purchasing%20the%20processed%20groundnuts%20at%20Rs%20100-120%20per%20kilogram%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20quality%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20prices%20they%20were%20getting.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20primary%20processing%20is%20now%20done%20by%20these%20farmers%2C%20they%20also%20have%20their%20own%20seeds%20to%20put%20back%20into%20harvesting%20the%20crop%20for%20the%20next%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20met%20Aman%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20how%20we%20could%20all%20work%20together%20for%20better%20profits.%20He%20brought%20us%20seeds%20and%20we%20worked%20on%20figuring%20out%20the%20best%20farming%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish%20Singh%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20our%20soil%20tested.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20was%20something%20you%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20do.%20Checking%20and%20regulating%20the%20pH%20levels%2C%20nitrogen%20phosphate%2C%20and%20carbon%2016%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20any%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20scientific%20perspective%2C%20Aman%20connected%20them%20with%20Dr%20Kishan%20Chandra%2C%20a%20scientist%20specialising%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20waste%20management%2C%20and%20bio-fertiliser%20production.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20a%20decomposer%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20mixture%20with%20water%20and%20essential%20nutrients%20that%20helps%20kill%20pests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manish%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202920px)%20100vw%2C%202920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aman%20Kumar%20and%20his%20co-founder%20pose%20with%20farmers%20at%20their%20primary%20processing%20space.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515.jpeg%202920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-